" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba88d9c29e30816d72c1b7ffe2b287939b876c34","tid":2488454,"uid":71711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:22:06.000Z","msg":"邊個再係到講海豚好cute就俾張gif佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ca76d0f8f1a112787f77503c5933bebb17d2a3","tid":2488454,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba88d9c29e30816d72c1b7ffe2b287939b876c34","tid":2488454,"uid":71711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:22:06.000Z","msg":"邊個再係到講海豚好cute就俾張gif佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"仲係好 cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56fd9c2fba37c16b48c1d5608b447047f5e662e","tid":2488454,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e8539db855516e983539a032e205a4c9c2e389","tid":2488454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:16:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">仲會吸毒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B5%B7%E8%B1%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A2%E8%87%AA%E6%85%B0%E9%82%84%E5%90%B8%E6%AF%92-%E5%97%A8%E7%88%86%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-080524902.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E8%25B1%259A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%2585%25B0%25E9%2582%2584%25E5%2590%25B8%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E5%2597%25A8%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-080524902.html&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=17eaf18b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B5%B7%E8%B1%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A2%E8%87%AA%E6%85%B0%E9%82%84%E5%90%B8%E6%AF%92-%E5%97%A8%E7%88%86%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-080524902.html</a><br />\n<br />\n海豚是世上智商最高的動物之一，不管在哪國都非常受到歡迎，不過海豚非常喜愛嬉鬧，除了性生活繽紛，會咬掉死魚的魚頭當作飛機杯自慰、同性性行為之外，牠們甚至還會將河豚含在口中藉此「吸毒」！近日英國《BBC》的自然紀錄片《荒野間諜》（Spy In The Wild）就在南非拍攝到罕見的「海豚吸毒」景像，近距離揭密海豚的生態。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒爆導，攝影團隊追蹤到一群平均約2歲的年輕公海豚，牠們因不守規矩被趕出原生族群，此後成群一起優游在大海中進行冒險；攝影團隊製作了內藏攝影機的「間諜烏龜」和「間諜河豚」，希望能近距離觀察海豚們和其他生物的互動，海豚紛紛開始把它們當成玩具進行衝撞，沒想到附近突然亂入一個活生生的真河豚，海豚們就漸漸將目標轉移到牠身上。<br />\n<br />\n由於河豚擁有劇毒的河魨毒素及箱魨毒素，能引發橫膈膜麻痺而引致呼吸困難甚至致死，只要一隻的毒素就足以殺死約三十個成人，大部分都儲存在河豚內臟，但皮膚上也含有部分毒素。<br />\n從影片中可以看到，海豚們紛紛把河豚當成玩具亂丟亂甩，甚至還玩心大起把牠丟到水面上，接著又一個接著一個搶著把河豚咬在口中「吸毒」，另一方面卻又小心翼翼的確保不要吞下或殺死河豚，以免自己中毒身亡，最後玩膩了後才把河豚放走、離開該處海域。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=0T5aGLybXEs&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0T5aGLybXEs%26feature%3Demb_title&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=630156c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=0T5aGLybXEs&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"d3fb322433a2f28d1eb20208a7395eed147209b4","tid":2488454,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec7ec2d1aaba13889768385f0e38e7540e09b40a","tid":2488454,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c477d9451c93f6847a0c194b0f65851700302279","tid":2488454,"uid":236171,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HtVGJ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HtVGJ0.png&h=fc243013&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:26:04.000Z","msg":"j完會唔會食埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食埋自己啲精"}]}